README for cvBlobDLL.


1. INTRODUCTION

This is a DLL C wrapper for cvBlob. You can use it to call "cvLabel" function 
of cvBlob from languages like Delphi and others. It translates the custom blob 
C++ object format of cvBlob to OpenCV types. This is also useful to call other 
OpenCV functions on blobs.


2. COMPILING

This is a Visual C++ 2008 express project. Make sure cvBlob is compiled, and 
libraries and includes paths are set right.


3. AUTHOR

